label.value: Savage, brutal, and deadly, the reaver is at home on the field of battle--and few places else.
The orc shaman has learned of plagues and venoms, and can put them to use restoring the forces of the dark lord or bring low the free people.
A deadly shot with his massive bow, the Uruk Blackarrow uses his considerable strength to send his quiver of foul, feathered arrows deep into his targets.
An impressive specimen of orc, the Uruk Warleader commands and directs forces in battle.
Using poisons and clinging webs, the weaver can manipulate and control her prey.
Silent and stealthy, the stalker strikes suddenly and does not offer escape for his foe.
